::Prowl::

Prowl grins at Iron Raptor, releasing her from his hold. He hadn't realize he 
was holding her tightly. He taps a few buttons on the side of the chamber, 
the door opening. Prowl looks back at Iron Raptor.

"Ok. Get healed from that Alliance experience," his eyes soften, Prowl 
looking at Iron Raptor with love in his optics, "Then I'll make you at home 
here."
